{"tid":856095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊岳橋：反對派錢，認為政府有責任利用手上盈餘，投資未來！","createTime":"2018-10-10T11:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T14:27:25.000Z","uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e873b97e2b247d8825a78f57286c73b8d5d48c75","tid":856095,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:40:52.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波將宣讀本屆政府首份財政預算案。工聯會立法會議員麥美娟說，政府坐擁龐大盈餘，這些盈餘主要來自賣地、股票及樓宇印花稅，基層市民大多不會參與，派錢可以令基層市民受惠。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席胡志偉認為，政府今次可以考慮派錢。民建聯主席李慧琼則說，派錢與否要視乎政府投放各方面資源後，是否仍有充裕盈餘。公民黨黨魁楊岳橋反對派錢，認為政府有責任利用手上盈餘，投資未來。<br />\n<br />\n退稅方面，大部分黨派贊成增加退稅上限，自由黨、民建聯、民主黨和工聯會，均建議上限應由去年2萬元，倍增至4萬元；新民黨則認為可以保持2萬元的退稅上限，公民黨就提出退稅3萬至3萬5000元。"},{"pid":"93dc70080b353bed81422a1c039a3ca41ea825b9","tid":856095,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae109b302006c76a609ea9764c591b99c150f05","tid":856095,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"鞭鞭有力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc644b65f813494a9c1d434cf6554f91c25da97f","tid":856095,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b635d8d33139de023d107d6c3364bc80f4ef07","tid":856095,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab9ae30e1c9a33b09986a36ad97ae3ca0fd7651","tid":856095,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:27:25.000Z","msg":"好鍾意睇on q呢條濕鳩"}]}